  "text": "We should emphasize that in what follows we view (7) as autonomous dynamical system with the traveling wave variable ξ playing the role of time (not to be confused with physical time). This allows us to use the language from [CITATION_1] dealing with singular perturbation problems in terms of multiple time scales. The terms fast, slow and others we will use are thus borrowed from the theory of dynamical systems and refer to ξ as \"time\".",
